lead_paragraph: Olympique Lyonnais need to shake off the psychological shock of the firecracker attack on their goalkeeper Anthony Lopes when they take on Sevilla in a must-win Champions League Group H finale on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Lyon Must Put Firecracker Trauma Behind Them in Group Finale
